ivate equity model of 40 years ago where people think you borrow as much as=
 you can, go play golf, and see if it all worked out in five years.=E2=80=
=9D Tennis clubs grapple with surge in demand for padel and pickleball. Wat=
ch a baseball game on the toilet.
