g canceled. A very strange corporate choice.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But it gets much stranger. The way SPACs work =
is:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">If the SPAC doesn=E2=80=99t complete =
