ockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I don=E2=80=99t know what to tell you. People =
sometimes worry that naked short sellers are going around creating =E2=80=
=9Cphantom shares=E2=80=9D in public companies to drive down the price and =
make trouble. That almost never actually happens. But it did here.</p>
