Stock Market is open 24/7 and institutional investors are actively=C2=A0<em=
>discouraged=C2=A0</em>from trading there, but if you want to, good luck, h=
ave fun.</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">It=E2=80=99s not perfect but it feels like the=
 right idea.</p>
