<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusine=
ss.com/click/35921520.194416/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS9maW5hbmNlL3N0b2Nrcy=
