<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Get a job.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin=
-bottom: 5px;">Steal from your employer.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom:=
 5px;">When you get fired, say =E2=80=9Cno, I have=C2=A0<em>committed a cri=
me</em>, and you can=E2=80=99t discriminate against me based on my criminal=
 record, so you can=E2=80=99t fire me.=E2=80=9D</li>
</ol>
